25th Aug 2014 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 3 Highlights

Stage 3 takes place in the province of Cadiz, this is slightly bumpier than yesterday's. The 189.8km route between Cadiz and Arcos de la Frontera features three third category climbs, and a climb at the end to break up the peloton before the finish. Presented by Gary Imlach, commentary by Anthony McCrossan and Graham Jones with Matt Rendell the reporter at the roadside.
